works.description:
The URLs listed below are carbon copies
of  
my own original work and have been used on a website that appears to mimic
 
an older version of my own site, using all of my writing along with  
everything else that was present on my site. They have used entire blog  
posts of mine without permission, and they have changed the author name  
to "Alex Steele" and "Adam Ledford" in various pages of the site.
